<L>__{interior. apartment day}
<A>__{lincoln enters, wary, scanning around. a living room. framed pictures. a sofa, chairs. a coffee table, empty bottles, cigarette packs, a full ashtray. a bureau, some paperwork. silence, stillness. no sign of life, no sense of danger. lincoln moves across to the bureau and starts leafing through the papers. ester ventures in through the door, curious }
