<C>__{tom}
<D>__{oh, jesus...}
<A>__{lincoln is better prepared for this encounter but still stunned by the sight of his double in the flesh. sponsor and agnate stand frozen. the only movement is ester, her eyes flicking between the same men, fraught, confused. lincoln breaks the silence }
