<C>__{tom}
<D>__{one of the partners at my firm... he told me about it. gave me a referral. i thought he was joking at first. i went out there, took the sales tour. even before that i knew it wasn't a joke. there was this discretion agree ment. i never saw anything like it and i've seen a lot. ironclad... breathe a word and they've got you by the balls. i don't know... there's cancer in my family. maybe it was just to keep up. all the partners were on the policy.}
